reviewText: Having this DVD is a big help it doesn't go to fast so it's easy to follow

Excellent video for beginners. Sharyn Pak takes time to go over all the basics as she is creating scrapbook pages. There is nothing boring about this video. After watching you can dive right in! I highly recommend this for newbies. If you want to learn how to scrapbook, this is a great resource.

As expected, Sharyn Pak has done it again. Sharyn's Scrapbooking DVD makes organized sense of the scrapbooking aisles in the crafts store. No longer am I overwhelmed by thousand bit and pieces of the craft, that always looked enticing, but I had no idea where to start. Now it's fun and gratifying.
